2.0.x-dev.name: mouf/utils.common.conditioninterface
2.0.x-dev.description: This package contains one interface for condition, and a few classes that implement it. For instance, AndCondition that requires all conditions to be met, and OrCondition that requires at least one condition to be met. A condition is a class that possesses an 'isOk' method. The condition returns true if the condition is met, and false otherwise.
